title: Why is Politics so messy? (Candace Owens and Russell Brand)
description:
This is in part a commentary on a clip of a conversation between Candace Owens and Russel Brand. I felt like this clip certainly displayed where we are at (at best) in modern politics. If we are gods, then we will fall. 

Hers's the clip: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TB7dQh_TpUc&t=211s

This is episode 41 of my podcast.
